Subject: [PATCH 1/2] setup.py: remove the setup_requires for setuptools-scm
Organization: O.S. Systems Software LTDA.

Use the same patch that pytest recipe from meta-python layer:

https://git.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded/plain/meta-python/recipes-devtools/python/python-pytest/0001-setup.py-remove-the-setup_requires-for-setuptools-scm.patch?h=warrior

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [oe specific]

Signed-off-by: Derek Straka <derek@asterius.io>
---
 setup.py | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/setup.py b/setup.py
index 0f26fa0..6568474 100644
--- a/setup.py
+++ b/setup.py
@@ -30,7 +30,6 @@ def main():
         description="plugin and hook calling mechanisms for python",
         long_description=long_description,
         use_scm_version={"write_to": "src/pluggy/_version.py"},
